Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:13.77,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Just count on me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.77,0:01:16.97,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}So what if sing off-key,who cares
