Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:23.84,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Let me go for my one true belief
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.08,0:01:25.43,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Overcome yourself
