Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.08,0:01:36.34,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}We'll be shining bright
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.34,0:01:37.89,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}No more fears      No more tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:39.27,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Everything will work out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.27,0:01:41.38,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}That's "God only knows"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:43.64,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Don't get me wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.76,0:01:45.36,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}This is not real love 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.59,0:01:48.84,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}But I'll do anying for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.94,0:01:51.69,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Whatever happens in my self,turn the page and come of age
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.44,0:01:54.67,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Remember,no one can judge me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.17,0:01:54.84,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Every and leads to a new beginning of the next stage
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:57.66,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Try to make my life complete ,trust myself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:02:00.17,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Be strong and do my best
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:04.94,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Don't look back,carry on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.94,0:02:07.77,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Be your self...Be happy...It's your life...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.47,0:02:09.24,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}"God only knows"
