Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須跟神大人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是乎
